        <mxCell id="tgi2q5tbjGthcWReG4RT-1" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;State: accounts and balances&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;Interface: create_account(), transfer(), withdraw(), create_state_checkpoint().&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;It contains all IPC-subnet logic for handling incoming messages and creating outward messages, such as MintDeposited(), Withdraw().&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;In&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Stage 1&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;this is instantiated by a Simulator, which is a mock implementation that handles/creates the required messages.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;In&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Stage 2&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;this will be Fendermint.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;" parent="1" vertex="1">
